Being familiar with these will save you a lot of hassle!
<ul>
<li><a href="http://ppc.wikia.com/wiki/PPC_Lounge">The PPC Lounge</a>
is the place for real-time chat. Pop in and see if anyone's around.</li>
<li><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/pub?id=18hztHpDehxcfrjaXoFUew1vb0BdZPDAusHxMHzHiCzM">The PPC Constitution</a> is Da Rules for our community.
<strong>Read this first</strong>, read it often, and follow it.</li>
<li><a href="http://ppc.wikia.com/wiki/PPC_Wiki">Our shiny PPC Wiki</a> will answer many of your questions.
<strong>Check before asking!</strong>
